data.description: This spacious Merced Heights home has two bedrooms, a bonus storage room and one bathroom. The home includes a  kitchen, bathroom, the entire place is turnkey ready to move in! The home offers city and ocean views from the living room, one indoor parking garage space, ample storage space and in unit washer & dryer. The home has a large backyard, with a redwood deck.    The home is located within walking distance to a transportation hub which includes the Balboa Bart Station, MUNI Streetcar lines and easy access to the 280/101 freeways. Downtown San Francisco is a 15 minute ride on bart. San Francisco State University and City College of San Francisco are near by. There are tons of restaurants/gyms/and other store fronts within walking distance such as Whole Foods Grocery, 24 Hour Fitness, Yoga studios, Walgreens, Peets coffee/Starbucks, Regal movie theater, etc.
